TextEng: Are you a prisoner here?
Stand back! I'll have no tricks out of you!
Calm down. I'm certainly not with Kurth.
Text: 진정해. 난 분명 커스 쪽이 아니야.

TextEng: You is prisoner here?
Stand back! No tricks!!
Me not with Kurth. You calm down now.
Text: 나 커스 쪽 아니야. 너 진정해.

TextEng: Of course I'm not one of Kurth's soldiers.
Me not Kurth soldier, no.
How do I know you're actually a prisoner, that this isn't some ruse?
Text: 네가 진짜 포로라는 걸 어떻게 알아, 이게 속임수가 아니라고?

TextEng: Just how did you end up here?
What reward would I get for letting you go?
Would you be able to find your way out on your own?
Text: 혼자 나갈 길을 찾을 수 있어?

TextEng: I'm not here to rescue you.
How I know you not lying?
Text: 너 거짓말 아닌 거 어떻게 알아?

TextEng: Just how you gets here?
Is there reward for freeing you?
You find way out on own?
Text: 너 혼자 나갈 길 찾을 수 있어?

TextEng: Me no rescuer.
Perhaps it's time I put you out of your misery, then.
Go, then, I could not care less.
I don't know. Is there anything in it for me for helping you?
Text: 모르겠어. 돕는 것에 대한 대가가 뭔데?

TextEng: Ha! Me puts you out of misery, then!
Text: 하! 나 너 고통에서 해방시켜 주겠어!

TextEng: Go, then, before me gets mad.
Don't know. What in it for me?
I don't trust you. Time to die!
No believe! Die! Die!!
You're of no use to me, then.
You no use to me, then.
You're Evaine, yes? I am here to rescue you.
I'm here to take you away. Don't give me any grief.
I'm freeing you, but I'm no babysitter. Can you get out on your own?
Text: 풀어줄 테니까, 근데 보호자는 아니야. 혼자 나갈 수 있어?

TextEng: Just stay there and don't move.
You Evaine? Me come to rescue.
Me here to take you out. No grief from you!
Text: 나 너 데려가러 왔어. 말썽 피우지 마!

TextEng: Me free you, but me no protector. You get out on own?
Text: 나 풀어줄게, 근데 나 보호자 아니야. 너 혼자 나갈 수 있어?

TextEng: Just stay and no move.
Then you can go.
Then you go, now.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Calm down. Just follow me and I'll bring you to Elynwyd, I promise.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 진정해. 날 따라와, 엘린위드에게 데려다줄게, 약속해.

TextEng: Stupid woman! If I have to drag you out, you're coming with me!
Text: 멍청한 여자! 질질 끌고라도 데려갈 거야!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You follow me, I bring you'se to Elynwyd, me promise.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 너 나 따라와, 나 너 엘린위드한테 데려가줄게, 약속해.

TextEng: Stupid woman! If me must drag you out, me will!
Text: 멍청한 여자! 나 끌고라도 데려갈 거야!

TextEng: I'll slit your throat if you don't do as I say! I am not joking!!
Text: 내 말 안 들으면 목을 그어버릴 거야! 농담 아니야!!

TextEng: Me slits your throat if you not come! Me no joke!!
Text: 나 안 오면 목 그어! 나 농담 아니야!!

TextEng: You can leave, then.
You goes, then.
